{"tid":420388,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無識日文嘅巴打幫幫手？","createTime":"2017-10-01T10:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T14:04:07.000Z","uid":134474,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a770715c2ed9dbd0277f24cbaff10f22f734192d","tid":420388,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/185539_e5ebb96cbf839b15257933046c9e3e2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F185539_e5ebb96cbf839b15257933046c9e3e2c.jpg&h=ed9732e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我整咗pat屎出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩仲有另外一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/185631_9a714bfc8edb70c3b6c2b77d2b551e2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F185631_9a714bfc8edb70c3b6c2b77d2b551e2e.jpg&h=da16faa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52de5d40f9aaf46596c255e913f9519fa49f3c57","tid":420388,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a31c984271070ce6649c01706f0f61e66c74a400","tid":420388,"uid":42256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:29:25.000Z","msg":"明呀 好長 唔想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你邊part唔識"},{"pid":"6d8867d7636368868ae202ed97a5912341b08b70","tid":420388,"uid":7840,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfacd96cfc0e43cf7dc7a8b33425dc686dc67afa","tid":420388,"uid":67480,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 拎隻碗裝1/4冰，加水之後浸8分鐘，或者自己雪一碗10度嘅水，碗水第5步要用，所以步驟2-4要係8分鐘之內完成。<br />\n2. 倒400ml水落鍋度，再倒1包100g餅粉，等餅粉完全沉底，其間不可攪動，可按喜好加30-100g糖<br />\n3. 開大火<br />\n4. 大火煲2-3分鐘，見到煲底嘅餅粉開始凝固，轉中火，之後攪下上面啲水，唔可以掂到煲底已經凝固左嘅餅粉，中火煲到餅粉完全凝固就熄火<br />\n5. 用匙羹切開煲底嘅餅，形狀大小自己喜歡，放落一開始果碗凍水度<br />\n6. 趁熱攞返上黎就食得，唔夠甜再加糖</blockquote><br />\n1嗰度係加水加到八分滿，唔係加水浸八分鐘<br />\n2嗰度係攪到啲粉溶晒冇晒一粒粒粉狀為止，唔係唔可以攪<br />\n3係開大火一路攪拌<br />\n4係一路keep住攪，攪到啲粉開始有黏性好似漿糊咁就轉中火，再繼續攪到佢去到好似麥芽糖咁上下嘅黏度就可以熄火<br />\n5係拎個匙羹依自己喜好一羹一羹咁挖出嚟，之後擺落去1預備好嘅冰水入面<br />\n6係攤凍之後就可以拎嚟食，可以加砂糖或者黃豆粉嚟食"},{"pid":"650eab39749295f81e6f8119e623bd214fe75b38","tid":420388,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"多謝哂咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}